title: Mission Rock win would be a blow to foes of Warriors’ arena
text:
Photo: Steelblue The design for the plaza at the proposed Warriors arena emphasizes open space. The design for the plaza at the proposed Warriors arena emphasizes...
While the political buzz in San Francisco is all about the Giants’ Mission Rock Project, it’s the Warriors’ arena development that is likely to put the first shovel in the ground.
